trong>Preferences</strong>. To remember your preferences and to recognize you when you return to evervault.</p><p><strong>Analytics</strong>. evervault uses <a href="https://analytics.google.com/">Google Analytics</a>, <a href="https://plausible.io/">Plausible</a>, and <a href="https://vercel.com/">Vercel</a> to collect information about how you interact with our website (e.g. page visits and link clicks), so we can improve your experience.</p><p><strong>Communications</strong>. We use <a href="https://intercom.com/">Intercom</a> as a channel for communications with our customers. In order to remember whether you had visited before and to keep track of existing conversations Intercom uses a cookie.</p><h2>Opting out</h2><p>You can customize your web browser to accept, reject, or delete cookies. All major browsers will give you the option to block some or all cookies and to clear existing cookie data.</p><p>Disabling necessary cookies may mean that some of evervault’s services will not function properly.</p><p>These links may be useful:</p><ul>
